import React from 'react';
import { Grid, Item, Header } from 'semantic-ui-react';

class MenuBar extends React.Component {

  render() {

    {/* Pull images from database */}
    return (
      <Grid>
        <Grid.Row>
          <Header style={{ 'font-size': '2em' }}>
            {this.props.title}
          </Header>
        </Grid.Row>
        <Grid.Row>
          <Grid.Column width={1}>
          </Grid.Column>
          <Grid.Column width={15}>

            <Item.Group>

              <Item>
                <Item.Image src='https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&source=images&cd=&ved=2ahUKEwjgqZnPxdDlAhVph-AKHTa7C3EQjRx6BAgBEAQ&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thespruceeats.com%2Foriginal-irish-coffee-recipe-759311&psig=AOvVaw3KRrH7SW7dnz1-792y-GKL&ust=1572956440972356' />

                <Item.Content>
                  <Item.Header as='a'>Hot Coffee</Item.Header>
                  <Item.Meta>Not your everyday cup of Joe.</Item.Meta>
                </Item.Content>
              </Item>

              <Item>
                <Item.Image src='https://www.google.com/imgres?imgurl=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.shopify.com%2Fs%2Ffiles%2F1%2F2627%2F1860%2Farticles%2Fwhat-is-the-best-cappuccino_1200x1200.jpg%3Fv%3D1558647494&imgrefurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wakacoffee.com%2Fblogs%2Fcoffeepedia%2Fwhat-is-cappuccino&docid=O9iWciyLPK28jM&tbnid=z7KnXAPRf7wVgM%3A&vet=10ahUKEwirypKNx9DlAhXySt8KHbVZAXgQMwiFASgMMAw..i&w=1080&h=1080&bih=821&biw=1440&q=cappuccino&ved=0ahUKEwirypKNx9DlAhXySt8KHbVZAXgQMwiFASgMMAw&iact=mrc&uact=8' />

                <Item.Content>
                  <Item.Header as='a'>Cappuccino</Item.Header>
                  <Item.Meta>Imported from Italy.</Item.Meta>
                </Item.Content>
              </Item>

              <Item>
                <Item.Image src='https://www.google.com/imgres?imgurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caffesociety.co.uk%2Fassets%2Frecipe-images%2Flatte-small.jpg&imgrefurl=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.caffesociety.co.uk%2Fhow-to-make-a-latte&docid=vDaXabBneZrjoM&tbnid=GOU1LV0MaXAYtM%3A&vet=10ahUKEwidm4fRx9DlAhWMiOAKHbunBrsQMwh5KAEwAQ..i&w=300&h=300&bih=821&biw=1440&q=latte&ved=0ahUKEwidm4fRx9DlAhWMiOAKHbunBrsQMwh5KAEwAQ&iact=mrc&uact=8' />

                <Item.Content>
                  <Item.Header as='a'>Latte</Item.Header>
                  <Item.Meta>Extra milk. Extremely rich.</Item.Meta>
                </Item.Content>
              </Item>
            </Item.Group>

          </Grid.Column>
        </Grid.Row>
      </Grid>
    );
  }
}

export default MenuBar;
